Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:11.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:17.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:30.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:36.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:44.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:51.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:01:00.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:05.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:10.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:15.78,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:22.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距今约一百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强因为担心吃坏肚子的娜蒂亚 因而外出采药
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却在某个洞穴内 吃下怪异的蕈类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,整个人都昏了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当天夜里娜蒂亚由衷感谢强 总是为她尽心尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是将初吻献给了强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚究竟在想些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:51.72,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,26 孤零零的大王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说 你完全不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只记得自己在洞穴里 发现会发光的蕈类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我做了什么惊人的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是非常不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不记得对你来说 或许比较幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我做了那么严重的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你居然什么都不记得了 娜蒂亚好可怜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好舒服 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到在这种地方 居然还有办法淋浴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的发明 如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉可以最后洗 不过 我要洗两次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒喔 强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你果然是个发明天才
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所谓的天才就是1%的灵感 与99%的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这句话是谁说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世纪的伟大发明家 强·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…洛克？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的亲戚？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要抢在别人之前说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为这种话是先说先赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给你 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用这个洗头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连洗发精都有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可不是普通的洗发精
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是用海草制成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还包含了润丝效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌 强好色喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好色？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚又变得不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 水停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 好像坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来得花一点时间才能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 真的好舒服 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等修好了 我再试用你的洗发精
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是平常她早就发脾气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会又吃了什么 坏掉的东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我用多出来的布做的 很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多出来的布？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,窗帘跑哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快说我很好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…非常好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你 强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再逃我可要不客气啰 别跑 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这家伙溜得可真快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无妨 最后手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看我的必杀诱导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何？认输了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过是个小宝宝 竟然敢跟我耍心机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邪恶是不可能当道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再抵抗也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就乖乖服从我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那这次来扮葛兰坦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉是葛兰坦 大王是人型战车喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气氛变得好祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉和大王感情还是那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚也没那么凶了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待在鹦鹉螺号上的那段时光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仿佛是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还得在这座岛 待上一段时日吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是说我们会一辈子 都在这座岛上生活？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要把这个放在耳边…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘘 我听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以听到海的声音喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要不要听听看？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听 可以听到海浪声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备好了吗？娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开…开始啰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会又突然停住吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为是我用手在转动的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何？看得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看是看得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 模模糊糊的 不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该不会那样才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的耶 都糊掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了 镜头不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为没有卡住镜头的零件 所以动不动就会掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微往右一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它动了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是地球在动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是月球在动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为地球以一天一周的速度自转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看起来就像是月球在动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自转？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是很久以前 由一位名叫哥白尼的科学家所发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之后经由伽利略证明的 『地动说』理论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这个理论被发现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都相信是空中的太阳 月亮或星星在动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伽利略就是利用这样的望远镜 证明理论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尽管因此遭到 周围人们的迫害…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听我说这些很无聊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会 你真是无所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还有许多必须去学习的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 都是托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们才能在这种地方撑到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是没有你 我早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总有一天 我一定会带你回你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和女生这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…是第一次吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么…我只是想知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是第二次！
