Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会是韩森？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别开玩笑了
