Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 是操舵长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轮机长？
