Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水准操作员？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好过份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了 是科学部长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你够了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问女孩子这种问题很失礼耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我初吻的对象竟然是这种人 真是差劲透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然…什么都不记得…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强是笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你居然什么都不记得了 娜蒂亚好可怜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是蕈类中毒的那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你身体不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 不好了 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王变成木头了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来像是留言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留言？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你看得懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呜喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上面写了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『我是动物』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『所以要暂时回归动物的世界』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『重新审视不够成熟的自己』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王\N大王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它到底是跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到这座岛这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 连山洞都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头有好多蕈类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕈类？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我本来想忘记的 你却害我又想了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强是笨蛋
