Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就把那件事付诸流水 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要跟着我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分成两路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟玛莉负责这座森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去那座山找
