Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种小山来个一两座 对你应该都是小意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那座山哪里小了…
