Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然还是行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么就是无法成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总是注定会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终究是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今日的失败 将造就明日的成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要拥有坚强的意志与信念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠自己的力量开拓可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼…尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,优秀的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是由99%的努力 与1%的灵感所构成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是美国的伟大发明家 汤玛斯·爱迪生的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要牢牢记住这句话 帮娜蒂亚实现梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别喊我舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原…原来是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王一定是吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃醋？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为娜蒂亚跟强的感情变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我全都晓得喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚喜欢强吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.76,0:23:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下子喜欢 一下子讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弄不懂自己的心情是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚的脸好红喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为夕阳的关系啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些话你是从哪里学来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王\N大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉喔抱歉喔 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么啦 强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.53,0:23:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一高兴眼镜就会掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.87,0:23:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一高兴眼镜就会…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.98,0:23:54.78,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:24:02.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.89,0:24:07.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:21.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:31.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:40.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.23,0:24:44.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.43,0:24:49.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.14,0:24:58.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.42,0:25:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,台风侵袭了林肯岛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.86,0:25:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的家 还有大王都被吹走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.23,0:25:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.83,0:25:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我向天空的流星祈祷了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祈祷了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.87,0:25:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望我们能找到大王
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.87,0:25:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望我们能早点离开这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.07,0:25:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『魔女所在之岛』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.64,0:25:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
